Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:02.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:04.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:07.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你又在和人类玩耍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类都很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:11.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:12.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:17.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们也是时候考虑和他们共存了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:20.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不好  人类袭击了我们龙族的村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:24.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们稍微安分点就立刻得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:28.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类  我决不饶恕你们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:35.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不能再和人类玩耍了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:36.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:40.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是人类杀害了你的双亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:43.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们不可能相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家都睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:29.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没想到除了爸爸以外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看到的第一个家伙会是自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是  很晚回家的话  提前说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:43.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:45.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么了  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你脸红了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:50.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么我会对这样的托尔心动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:01.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,难不成我对托尔发情了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,总之你先穿上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:04.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:08.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只要你变成了男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:13.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,会立刻暴露本性的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,让我见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类有多肤浅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:19.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她一定在想这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:23.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,应该是伊露露用魔法将我变成了男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果能随着时间流逝恢复就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道伊露露对我有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我只要保持平常心就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:54.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,早上好  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为我觉得早上很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:02.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:10.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,现在这样真不知道会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,必须和大家保持距离
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能不能让托尔帮我变回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林变成雄性了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来做繁衍种族的行为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:26.82,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,65)}乘上独木舟去冒险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.66,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,65)}电视机前的大家也一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,教育节目
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.51,0:04:28.87,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：此处捏他自NHK播放的一档教育节目《シャキーン》。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:32.91,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:34.87,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,快划快划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:39.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:43.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有瀑布  大家抱紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明这种事  女生之间做很正常的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我能忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不能被那些不知所谓的本能所支配
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:56.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别缠着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别缠着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:05.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以我说了  别随便抱过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:06.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她以前跟我有这么多肢体接触吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:23.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太好了  变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然伊露露因为和托尔的战斗而变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:33.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在托尔的世界中她所属的势力…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是叫混沌势力来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:39.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他们憎恨人类  并如此教育自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:43.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露就在这种环境中成长并且活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就变成了现在的心境
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜已经睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要来晚酌一两杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:05.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,现在就先不要想这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,之前好像也有过这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:15.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是春药？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:20.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我刚才就察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:24.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林现在是带把儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:27.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是被伊露露施法了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可怜的小林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就由托尔来为你治好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔必须抓住机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在心灵相通之后  就该是身体交融了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来吧  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一切都交给托尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么你突然好萎靡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你竟然把女仆装脱掉  不带这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔  我要以男性的视角
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,把女仆的优点从头到尾给你讲清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:00.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已经撑过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下一步你准备怎么办呢  伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小姐  装饰得真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,总感觉有哪里不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:28.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Comment: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.97,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,第2话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.97,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur10\pos(988.8,594.8)}帅哥小林！（各种意义上）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,站住  不准逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你咋这么能追  调和势力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是屠龙派的克莱梅内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:56.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当你死的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在冥界的审判记得报上我的这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好让我立功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:08.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露总是在我独自一人的时候出现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就这么等着能见到她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:17.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我好像对伊露露很执着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是因为觉得可以跟她交好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:27.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,至今为止遇到的异界人都很友好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:32.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明像是经历了无数纷争及其所导致的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是却还愿意接触人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是因为她们认为世界不只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:42.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一定有战争以外的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我相信着这样的托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:50.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以我才想要和伊露露和解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露没有出现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没准她在路人少的这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:06.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,被看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:14.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个世界的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:18.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我为屠戮这只异世界的害兽而来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,速速离开此处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,离开这里并就此忘却此事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是来杀伊露露的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明是大人却要杀一个小孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:32.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她是混沌派
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是只会给人类带来灾害的邪龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:40.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:48.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这噪音令人如此不悦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:51.73,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,防狼警报器  助我一臂之力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:01.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,重死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然让她逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:06.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么人类会救她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,外伤好像很快就愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:21.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你为什么要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,现在还不能说得救了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那家伙一定会追过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:28.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果我在战斗中输了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:34.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那也是我的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么被我救下来了  也算是你的命运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:43.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是想向我宣泄什么情绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我在与你的交流中隐约察觉到这点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:54.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不认可跟人类共存的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,龙不可能跟人类和谐共处的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你之前就说过这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我至今为止的人生就为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.44,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,身为高等存在的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.32,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,与人类交好简直是耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:15.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.86,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,发生了这么多起悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.70,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,和解是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:20.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:22.53,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,人类是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:23.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想要继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:24.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:38.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想要继续一起玩耍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然而谁都不允许我这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明那两个孩子什么错都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:52.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:59.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那下次我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:04.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们一起经历过了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:08.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,玩躲避球  逛漫展  去泡温泉等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:13.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然并不亚于战斗的嬉戏还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只是想说些漂亮话来哄骗我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:20.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我正试图用些花言巧语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:27.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来驯化你这头凶恶且混沌的邪龙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你要选择相信过往的教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还是选择被我欺骗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没想到人类也是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:52.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你也要清除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:53.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你们不是有规矩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,规矩早就形同虚设了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而且这是龙与龙之间的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不适用于人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:08.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如此对比  托尔她爸爸还真是仁慈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:09.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别太小瞧人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然还有企图保护龙的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:22.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:31.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,超痛的  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来得太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你居然敢对小林动手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:56.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就算有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我叫援军来也能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我这就叫艾尔玛大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你要是好好求饶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:08.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就只毁你肉身  放过你的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来  求饶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你杀掉他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没有  我只是消除了有关这个世界的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后扔回原来的世界去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,稍微教训下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&HE0CDB7&\pos(427.2,240.6)}角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:36.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样伊露露也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,放下心来以后  怎么感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,龙的唾液有止血功效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你只是想舔小林吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:51.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来吧小林  让我舔舔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你这舌头也太长了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,身为一名上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:04.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就要一味地认真执行规定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,公司优先于个人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我曾经是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:16.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为我总被教导自己有义务尽全力去完成工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:18.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等我回过神来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,私交的朋友都已不在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而在此时  我邂逅了托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:27.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,自己才发生了改变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:30.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以  伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:34.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可能是把你看成从前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:41.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:42.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对  伤口也已经愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:51.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么扯都拉不开她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这么晚才察觉到小林的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:07.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我能被你欺骗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:33.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天由我厄尔尼诺·三木播报全国的天气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,爪子还有尾巴等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不收起来没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.97,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,今日的大部分地区都是晴空万里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还有胸也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:41.07,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,因为处于高气压的影响下将会出现大范围的晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:41.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在日常生活很不方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:44.19,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,所以可以放心地晒衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别看伊露露这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:45.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她保持现在这个身形已经是很勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.11,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,同时也到了樱花的花季
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是不勉强自己的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那对胸会更大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但爪子和尾巴应该能随时收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:55.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那为什么惟独胸部不能收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,分个至少5%给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:50.99,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,因为处于开花初期所以这个时期还没有这么多蚊虫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:56.41,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,那么趁机今天去赏樱也是个不错的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.16,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,早上可能会有点冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:01.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:03.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是在这里排尿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,得从这里开始教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对  坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:10.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看来还有很多东西得教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:20.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是这时候有个优秀的女仆就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我会对她刮目相看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:26.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只要在我工作的时候照顾她就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:33.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我和小林要白头偕老的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别若无其事地说什么白头偕老
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:41.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你的肌肉有在锻炼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.62,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,肌肉不加锻炼就会减少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:44.79,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,会促进机体衰老…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她可是不久前还在相互厮杀的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:51.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔绝对不会原谅背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要被肃清了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是我还想了解小林更多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:57.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可没这么容易被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不准打架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:03.56,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b0\c&H4C4D48&\frz45.26\pos(918.666,542)}如何与人类生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:03.56,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b0\c&H4C4D48&\frz47.33\pos(1216,743.333)}小林托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:03.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是我写的如何作为一个人类生活的指南手册
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,先把爪子变成人类的手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,笑这么邪恶干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你连手都不会变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:29.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我变不好  就这样用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这双手能抓住东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像上面长有很多小手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:34.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:41.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类通过「打招呼」来交流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:45.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,总之记住重复对方向你打招呼说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:46.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类基本什么都吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:52.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但不喜欢吃龙肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:54.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,正在寻找可以让人类吃下龙肉的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:56.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:57.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这内容的主观性太强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这可是我心中的真实想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:06.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,衣服要尽量穿得和人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样才不会很显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你穿的跟普通人有些不太一样啊
Comment: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/The  异类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:16.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也穿个适合人类穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这里没有适合你的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是有康娜的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以说尺寸不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:22.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你看  有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是不听话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:29.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,跟我一样  用鳞片变成衣服如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我做不到这么巧妙的本领
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:35.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就借我的衣服来穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:38.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你接下来打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:41.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是想你做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没什么想做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想做的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,让我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:49.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:53.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在想好之前  可以在这个家里待到你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,赶紧滚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,客套话都没说全呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能你会觉得意外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:02.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我十分不情愿让你留在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一点都不意外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:07.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为你想想  自己是以什么形象出场的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,仿佛是个嗜血的狂战士哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:13.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是因为和托尔战斗很有趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:14.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不对  我当时是这种表情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,请快点找到你想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:21.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,正所谓「不劳者不得食」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:22.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那康娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜在做一份名为「小学生」的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我也做那份叫「小学生」的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:31.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,必须得是小孩才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你和我同龄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:35.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,尽情苦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:43.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,说是在思考想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但愿能找到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:20:59.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:01.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我找到自己总之想做的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:03.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想和小林造小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想了下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我已经到养儿育女的年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:14.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我缺少家人所产生的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想要让小林来填满
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:18.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林和我造小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:20.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:21.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这可不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,万万不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:24.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而且我是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我再给你装上就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:28.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行  要造也是和我造
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:30.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下流
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.06,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:35.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然我的贞操没人要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但也绝不会给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:44.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是伊露露的
Comment: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,---ED---
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:22.46,Kobayashi S2 - Next,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\pos(961.333,664.667)}下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:24.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露睡哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:26.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没法再塞多张床了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:27.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这里怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:28.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,壁橱？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:29.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,让人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.39,0:23:30.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露觉得好就行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.64,0:23:32.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我很中意
Comment: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:34.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/第三话
