Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.98,0:23:38.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,本周堕落的是谁呢
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.75,0:23:39.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,巨蟹座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(879.999,684.667)}可能会被卷入意外事件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(778.667,732.667)}幸运建议
